      <title>官員稱哈馬斯確認其代表團將於週六訪問開羅</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/hamas-confirms-its-delegation-visit-cairo-saturday-official-says-2024-05-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名哈馬斯官員告訴路透社，巴勒斯坦激進組織哈馬斯的代表團將於週六訪問開羅，預計他們將對以色列關於加薩停火和釋放人質的提議做出書面回應。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/hamas-confirms-its-delegation-visit-cairo-saturday-official-says-2024-05-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 18:19:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
